title: Online Lenders vs. Banks: Who Gets Disrupted?
text:
The future of marketplace lenders may be a thing of the past.
Online lending sites like LendingClub and On Deck Capital are at the vanguard of so-called fintech companies destined, according to enthusiasts, to disrupt traditional banks. Yet that proposition looks increasingly dubious.
